title: Production of Oats in Canada 2019
summary: The graph illustrates the Production of Oats in Canada the year 2019 .
The Production is very low in the first third of the year , before it rises sharply until October , reaching a maximum of 20000 Tonnes .
Then the Production decreased again for the remaining months of the year .
gold: The graph depicts the production of oats in Canada in 2019 . The production generally falls from January to July . It then climbs rapidly to the peak at over 400000 tonnes in October .
